==English==
===Noun===
'''spectacles''' ''plural''

#Plural of [[spectacle]].
# (''always plural'') A pair of [[lens]]es set in a frame worn on the nose and ears in order to correct deficiencies in [[eyesight]] or to ornament the face.

====Variant form====

====Synonyms====
*[[eyeglasses]] (''US'')
*[[glasses]]
*[[pair of eyeglasses]] (''US'')
*[[pair of glasses]]
*[[pair of specs]] (''colloquial'')
*[[pair of spectacles]]
*[[specs]] (''colloquial'')

